              <DefinitionShort>pertaining to that which is easy to bear or endure</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>light</Gloss>
                <Gloss>easy</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is possible to render ἐλαφρός in {S:04001103000020} as ‘light,’ in the sense of ‘light in weight’ (see {D:86.2}). However, if ‘burden’ in {S:04001103000020} is understood figuratively, ἐλαφρός can generally also be understood in a figurative sense.</Comments>
